  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/029d1cf017b490a37060a585322b1316.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/029d1cf017b490a37060a585322b1316.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>Visit our camp to seek help from one of the fantasy fighters, and delve into the brick-breaking adventure. Collect gems and coins to upgrade your heroes, aiding you in facing dangerous enemies along your journey. Break barricades and get to the enemy side to beat them once and for all.<br><br>Tiny Breakers Camp is an indie game that combines the classic Brick Breaker action with Rogue-lite experience. The game features meta-progression for heroes and a linear campaign where players can unlock new spells and skills—all set in an adorable, fantasy pixel world. A mix like no other.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Choose your hero.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/e85d52b5d4560392de8c5d6b491a4aa1.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=378 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/e85d52b5d4560392de8c5d6b491a4aa1.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/e85d52b5d4560392de8c5d6b491a4aa1.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul>Every hero has his own special attack, health pool and talent for magic.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><strong>Break the barricades on the battlefield.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/bba293f210dbe70525772be79d74c97d.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=180 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/bba293f210dbe70525772be79d74c97d.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ea6a312e990c49d0b966f54dafc21212.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ea6a312e990c49d0b966f54dafc21212.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/3c1dfbb4dbec4164fdf7565e050078a9.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=96 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/3c1dfbb4dbec4164fdf7565e050078a9.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/53ae61aa446cad95c0c1544c29c71eb2.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/53ae61aa446cad95c0c1544c29c71eb2.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span></ul>You will face many obstacles on the battlefield, boxes, chest, books or gems. Destroy them to open you a way and defeat your enemy. Plan your attack carefully because some obstacles are indestructible.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Collect all goodies.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/d986620fdf0abe7faedd2e68ed5c75e6.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/d986620fdf0abe7faedd2e68ed5c75e6.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b42650a82588d10889d9be0e0c1b60dd.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b42650a82588d10889d9be0e0c1b60dd.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8ab5e8678cf3a805856b2ee1e15f3040.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=96 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8ab5e8678cf3a805856b2ee1e15f3040.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8ab5e8678cf3a805856b2ee1e15f3040.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul>Try to catch all falling treasures, spells and buffs. You can spend coins and gems to upgrade your heroes. Cast powerful spells or even bring a support on the battlefield.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ee702bb231f1516eefd7c53f592a6722.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ee702bb231f1516eefd7c53f592a6722.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><strong>Beat your enemies!</strong></h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/2a451f31864d9275a435a7a124618eff.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=300 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/2a451f31864d9275a435a7a124618eff.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/2a451f31864d9275a435a7a124618eff.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ed2aa4844e0d9ddbb547e8f7c5c30d6c.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ed2aa4844e0d9ddbb547e8f7c5c30d6c.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=72 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/dc100f3993af79a74eaac71cb7fdf44c.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=96 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/dc100f3993af79a74eaac71cb7fdf44c.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></ul>Enemies have their own spells and minions. If you want to survive the mission, use all your arsenal to deal with them quickly.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Liberate your land in challenging campaign.</strong></h2></ul>Uncover spells and buffs by beating campaign missions in this tiny fantasy world. You can also play random missions to collect more gems and coins. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8700ebbe1f493e7c08dd1e6d7eaaa3ce.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8700ebbe1f493e7c08dd1e6d7eaaa3ce.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8700ebbe1f493e7c08dd1e6d7eaaa3ce.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><strong>Go and get them Hero!</strong></h2></ul><br>BUM!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/833ad6877d4fdd0f585363bfc9564b4e.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/833ad6877d4fdd0f585363bfc9564b4e.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/833ad6877d4fdd0f585363bfc9564b4e.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BAM!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/4125b82227aa8a6ad70a8dbc045c6225.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/4125b82227aa8a6ad70a8dbc045c6225.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/4125b82227aa8a6ad70a8dbc045c6225.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>...and Win!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/147a6bba7a1db7a75dc5863ee49ae988.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/147a6bba7a1db7a75dc5863ee49ae988.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/147a6bba7a1db7a75dc5863ee49ae988.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Controls:</strong></h2>Enjoy your game playing with keyboard or game controller if you like, Tiny Breakers Camp supports both.</ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/029d1cf017b490a37060a585322b1316.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/029d1cf017b490a37060a585322b1316.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>Visit our camp to seek help from one of the fantasy fighters, and delve into the brick-breaking adventure. Collect gems and coins to upgrade your heroes, aiding you in facing dangerous enemies along your journey. Break barricades and get to the enemy side to beat them once and for all.<br><br>Tiny Breakers Camp is an indie game that combines the classic Brick Breaker action with Rogue-lite experience. The game features meta-progression for heroes and a linear campaign where players can unlock new spells and skills—all set in an adorable, fantasy pixel world. A mix like no other.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Choose your hero.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/e85d52b5d4560392de8c5d6b491a4aa1.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=378 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/e85d52b5d4560392de8c5d6b491a4aa1.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/e85d52b5d4560392de8c5d6b491a4aa1.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul>Every hero has his own special attack, health pool and talent for magic.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><strong>Break the barricades on the battlefield.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/bba293f210dbe70525772be79d74c97d.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=180 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/bba293f210dbe70525772be79d74c97d.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ea6a312e990c49d0b966f54dafc21212.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ea6a312e990c49d0b966f54dafc21212.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/3c1dfbb4dbec4164fdf7565e050078a9.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=96 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/3c1dfbb4dbec4164fdf7565e050078a9.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/53ae61aa446cad95c0c1544c29c71eb2.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/53ae61aa446cad95c0c1544c29c71eb2.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span></ul>You will face many obstacles on the battlefield, boxes, chest, books or gems. Destroy them to open you a way and defeat your enemy. Plan your attack carefully because some obstacles are indestructible.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Collect all goodies.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/d986620fdf0abe7faedd2e68ed5c75e6.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/d986620fdf0abe7faedd2e68ed5c75e6.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b42650a82588d10889d9be0e0c1b60dd.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b42650a82588d10889d9be0e0c1b60dd.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8ab5e8678cf3a805856b2ee1e15f3040.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=96 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8ab5e8678cf3a805856b2ee1e15f3040.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8ab5e8678cf3a805856b2ee1e15f3040.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul>Try to catch all falling treasures, spells and buffs. You can spend coins and gems to upgrade your heroes. Cast powerful spells or even bring a support on the battlefield.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ee702bb231f1516eefd7c53f592a6722.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ee702bb231f1516eefd7c53f592a6722.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><strong>Beat your enemies!</strong></h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/2a451f31864d9275a435a7a124618eff.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=300 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/2a451f31864d9275a435a7a124618eff.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/2a451f31864d9275a435a7a124618eff.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ed2aa4844e0d9ddbb547e8f7c5c30d6c.apng?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/ed2aa4844e0d9ddbb547e8f7c5c30d6c.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=72 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/dc100f3993af79a74eaac71cb7fdf44c.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=96 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/dc100f3993af79a74eaac71cb7fdf44c.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></ul>Enemies have their own spells and minions. If you want to survive the mission, use all your arsenal to deal with them quickly.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/5326cf2f6f5316da67b648b29b978761.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Liberate your land in challenging campaign.</strong></h2></ul>Uncover spells and buffs by beating campaign missions in this tiny fantasy world. You can also play random missions to collect more gems and coins. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8700ebbe1f493e7c08dd1e6d7eaaa3ce.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8700ebbe1f493e7c08dd1e6d7eaaa3ce.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/8700ebbe1f493e7c08dd1e6d7eaaa3ce.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.gif?t=1728897017\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/b1ecc38bfe093f9d8dbf3f15edabe0d5.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><strong>Go and get them Hero!</strong></h2></ul><br>BUM!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/833ad6877d4fdd0f585363bfc9564b4e.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/833ad6877d4fdd0f585363bfc9564b4e.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/833ad6877d4fdd0f585363bfc9564b4e.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BAM!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/4125b82227aa8a6ad70a8dbc045c6225.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/4125b82227aa8a6ad70a8dbc045c6225.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/4125b82227aa8a6ad70a8dbc045c6225.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>...and Win!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/147a6bba7a1db7a75dc5863ee49ae988.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/147a6bba7a1db7a75dc5863ee49ae988.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/147a6bba7a1db7a75dc5863ee49ae988.mp4?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.poster.avif?t=1728897017\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619900/extras/c4fa0cf4b0e9ccecfa855c0149fed6c8.webm?t=1728897017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Controls:</strong></h2>Enjoy your game playing with keyboard or game controller if you like, Tiny Breakers Camp supports both.</ul>",
